v0.4.4 (The Access-And-Control Update)

first purchase of "water 1 plot" garden upgrade is much cheaper

reduced price scaling of "water 1 plot" and "enrich 1 plot" garden upgrades

shop/settings interactions while moving are now only disabled when the player has a touch screen that is also enabled in the settings

added gamepad support for movement and interaction with stick-drift accomodation

modified player movement

fixed a bug where passing over a shop/settings item would automatically interact if the interact button was pressed beforehand

clamped the distance in which the player can exit the game area

clamped rabbits and turtles to remain on screen (They would mysteriously disappear, and I never saw how)

reduced and tweaked many tooltip messages
